<paragraph base="F4230906" principles="no" id="IFRS03_B5"><paranum>B5</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 3"/><data name="paranum" value="B5"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS03_P0331">This IFRS defines a <xref base="F4230842" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0304">business combination<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0025"/></ph></xref> as a transaction or other event in which an <xref base="F4230833" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0297">acquirer<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0005"/></ph></xref> obtains <xref base="F4230846" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_APPA.dita#IFRS10_APPA/IFRS10_DI0002" scope="local">control<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0053"/></ph></xref> of one or more <xref base="F4230839" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0301">businesses<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0024"/></ph></xref>. An acquirer might obtain control of an <xref base="F4230829" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0296">acquiree<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0004"/></ph></xref> in a variety of ways, for example:</p><ol base="F4230909" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS03_L0033"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F4230910" id="IFRS03_P0332">by transferring cash, cash equivalents or other assets (including net assets that constitute a business);</p>       </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F4230912" id="IFRS03_P0333">by incurring liabilities;</p>       </li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p base="F4230914" id="IFRS03_P0334">by issuing <xref base="F4230851" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0308">equity interests<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0104"/></ph></xref>;</p>       </li><li><li_value>(d)</li_value>         <p base="F4230916" id="IFRS03_P0335">by providing more than one type of consideration; or</p>       </li><li><li_value>(e)</li_value>         <p base="F4230918" id="IFRS03_P0336">without transferring consideration, including by contract alone (see <xref base="F5479544" href="IFRS03_43.dita#IFRS03_43" id="IFRS03_X0390">paragraph 43</xref>).</p>       </li></ol></body></paragraph>